**Operating system or device - Godot version:**
win - current master

Issue:
Calling get_selected_node_list in "selection_changed"-signalled function results in endless loop.

as seen below get_selected_node_list calls update(), 
but update fires selection_changed,
which again fires update();

EDIT:
this fixed it for me, but i dont have tested it much:

```
void EditorSelection::update() {

	_update_nl();

	if (!changed)
		return;
        //////////////////////////////////////////////
	changed = false; 
	emit_signal("selection_changed");
        //////////////////////////////////////////////
}
```
original source:
```
void EditorSelection::update() {

	_update_nl();

	if (!changed)
		return;
	emit_signal("selection_changed");
	changed = false;
}

List<Node *> &EditorSelection::get_selected_node_list() {

	if (changed)
		update();
	else
		_update_nl();
	return selected_node_list;
}
```
